	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Home</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<div class='code-block code-block-1' style='margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;'>
<script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-0665173920649568"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script></div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;"><u>AREA HAZARD CONTROL NIG. LIMITED WAS INCORPORATED UNDER THE COMPANIES AND ALLIED MATTERS ACT 1990 AND THAT THE COMPANY IS LIMITED BY SHARES.</u></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">AREA HAZARD CONTROL which was registered in 2006. The company’s activities involve in engineering, marine equipment leasing, electrical works, construction, maintenance, support and management services onshore and offshore to Nigeria energy oil and as industries these activities are backed up technically by well established high skill personnel. </span></strong></span><br />
<span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">Within its short period of existences in the oil industry AREA HAZARD CONTROL LIMITED has demonstrated that it is a Nigeria company whose major goal is result and customers satisfaction only our firm commitment to timely problems solving will provide you with non going value and peace of mind. </span></strong></span><br />
<span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">AREA HAZARD CONTROL LIMITED will always respond to your call expected solution to your problems in an unbelievable reaction time. </span></strong></span><br />
<span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">On any job function AREA HAZARD CONTROL LIMITED deploy a unique combination of local and foreign professionals to deliver excellent and effective solution to problem. Our policy of involving the best available locals, in all trades with rigorous supervision provides us safe working environment without compromising on quality influential stakeholders are represented on Board.                                            </span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">       &#8221;   OUR MISSION  &#8220;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">      To be first among real indigenous Nigeria oil indigenous</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">     Nigeria oil services Company with international</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">    stature that employs self – motivated, highly</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">   skilled hands – on professional who are</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">always at the cutting edge with </span></strong></span></p>
